WinterGOAHistorical 0.1.0
  • Reference

    Pre-selectivity corrected dataset consisting of pollock biomass & numbers at age on a per-interval basis. Winter GOA.

    PreSelectivityWinterGOAages.Rd

    Pre-selectivity corrected dataset consisting of pollock biomass & numbers at age on a per-interval basis. Winter GOA.

    PreSelectivityWinterGOAages

    Format

    A data frame with 236399 rows and 16 columns:

    Ship

    ship number; 21 is MF, 157 is DY (numeric)

    Survey

    survey number (numeric)

    DataSetID

    Duh (numeric)

    AnalysisId

    Duh (numeric)

    ReportNumber

    The report number associated with the ages (numeric)

    Interval

    Original interval number, not unique in older surveys (numeric)

    Age

    Age of fish (years), determined by age & growth

    Transect

    Original transect designation; NULL transects were removed from these data

    Description

    The original descriptor in old MB

    Numbers

    Numbers of fish in that edsu

    Biomasskg

    Biomass (kg) of fish in that edsu

    START_TIME

    Date and Time (UTC) at the start of the interval

    Region

    Region in which the survey was performed, used st_join(st_within) from the sf library and updated geographic regions stored in: 'G://ARCVIEW//exported_shapefiles//winter_survey_regions_BarnabasChiniak_NAD1983' to determine survey area

    Latitude

    Latitude at start of edsu; older surveys don't have an end lat/long

    Longitude

    Longitude at start of edsu; older surveys don't have an end lat/long

    Year

    Year of Survey

    #' @source Historic MACE reported values
